data.description: Spacious former Pulte model home in Retama Ridge is now for sale.  Recently updated 4-bedroom home with functional floor plan.  Split master bedroom down provides space & privacy.  Spread out across the 2 living spaces where the downstairs fireplace adds warmth & ambiance to this cavernous space & its 17-foot ceilings.  The upstairs game room is a place for comfortable retreat.  Cooks will appreciate gas-cooking, stainless steel appliances, tall cabinetry, & solid counters.  Entertain guests in your formal dining room at the front of the home or enjoy a casual meal in the sizable eat-in kitchen space near the patio door.  Recent updates include newly installed carpet, glossy entry tile, & fresh paints adds to the turnkey nature of this home.  Shingles are little more than a year old and foundation repaired with transferable warranty.   Perched near the top of the hill, the large deck with pergola provides good views and extends the bountiful living space. Great curb appeal with the brick and stone front.  Ideal location on a quiet cul-de-sac Conveniently located near Loop 1604 & I-35 makes for quick trips to Randloph, The Forum, SAT airport, & HEB.  With its great curb appeal, ideal location, and thoughtful updates, this Retama Ridge beauty is a must see pick.
